Enum UserOption

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<UserOption>
      • enums.UserOption
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<UserOption>

    public enum UserOption
extends java.lang.Enum<UserOption>
    Enum for all options that are available to users. Permissions for what each user can do are handled in the controllers.
